commit.message:
bugfix: polymorphic inlines broken if nested in non-polymorphic inlines

Fixes #183

Polymorphic admin functionality was broken if a polymorphic inline was
nested within a non-polymorphic model. The existing tests only checked
cases where all inlines were polymorphic.

Remove inline permissions tests that broke after 2.1.15 and 2.2.8

It is no longer possible to edit inlines if the user has only view
permissions on the parent model.

See https://www.djangoproject.com/weblog/2019/dec/02/security-releases/
